{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究功与速度的关系。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">动能定理：合力对物体做的功等于物体动能的改变量。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桌面、垫木、带橡皮筋的长木板、小车、打点计时器。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.安装好实验装置，在属性中点击调平，自动平衡摩擦力；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.点击</span>&ldquo;弹射&rdquo;，打点计时器开始打点，小车开始运行，数据自动录入到表格中；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.点击重置，并将橡皮筋条数改为</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.点击</span>&ldquo;弹射&rdquo;，打点计时器开始打点，小车开始运行，数据自动录入到表格中；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.重复刚才操作，依次将橡皮筋条数改为</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;，并得到相应数据；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">6.点击表格，在属性中选择</span>&ldquo;显示图象&rdquo;；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">7.在图象中选择合适的类型及数据，做出橡皮筋做的功与速度的图象及橡皮筋与速度的平方的图象。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">橡皮筋做的功与速度的平方成正比。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实验所用的橡皮筋应为同一规格；实验开始时需要平衡摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}